Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I can't do it." "It's too frustrating."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Break down those hurdles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is nothing I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is being manipulated on the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not frightened yet I get told to go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The path to the unseen future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I may not be able to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Close your eyes, and shuffle your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As promised, yes! you are the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never lose! Shuffle your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since that miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ninja Master Magnum Arrives"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as we go by car!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get out! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? We're gonna walk the rest of the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stadium's the location of the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba and some other guys must be there by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this stadium must be the center of the Amusement City Kaiba Corporation's building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Kaiba Corporation for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They do everything in a big way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with all these finished buildings around, it's almost like walking in a ghost town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gives me the creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no hope of winning the finals if you're scared {\i1}this{\i0} easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\i1}sorry{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've been meaning to ask you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you do that back in the Duelist Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stand up, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Save those tears for if you lose the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just a runny nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It won't stop coming...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just clean it up. It's disgraceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi, don't give up on your desires so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those tears for your little sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, a {\b0}runny nose{\b1}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't give up on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's sure to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you give me that back then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I give you my card?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can tell you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious that it's because we're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Jean-Claude Magnum Ninja Series!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, I wish this movie would hurry up and open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a {\i1}huge{\i0} fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God... You didn't listen to a {\i1}word{\i0} I said...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the {\i1}hell{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you! That's dangerous, ya know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't a movie or somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I sure am sorry about that, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jean-Claude Magnum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! How do you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me... Y-You no... Very Very Fan de!\N [I'm a very big fan of yours in very poor Engrish]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}, I came to pick you up, just like we promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mistaking me for someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}awesome{\i0}, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know a {\i1}Hollywood star{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you he's mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}! Have you really forgotten our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. A promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Direct Attack Mr. Magnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whip Banish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Life has been drained to 0!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seems even a {\b0}Hollywood star{\b1} can't beat me in a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You plan to use your "ninja arts" to assault your Dueling rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai Kujaku, I have been completely subdued by your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai-{\b0}san{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll listen to your sick jokes after you beat me in a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So if I beat you in a Duel, it'll be okay to marry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though it's about 100 years too soon for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I {\i1}did{\i0} meet you once before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I plan to beat you and bring you back to Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go deciding that on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about, Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}Hollywood star{\i0} just proposed to you! You're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skip the Dueling part and just marry the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to marry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'd be freakin' cool to have one of my friends the wife of a Hollywood star!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My god...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's such a {\b0}kid{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll accept this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! So if I win the Duel, you'll marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan to {\i1}beat{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we forget about this and head for the location of the finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our spots in the finals could be taken over if we don't get over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...doesn't seem to plan on letting us go if she doesn't accept the Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} we're talking about! She'll finish this up soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you suggesting I {\i1}lose{\i0} before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right. Lend him your Duel Disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Duel Disk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only members of the highest ranks are permitted one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am among those highest ranking members.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I have already obtained five Puzzle Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means if Mai-san loses, she won't be able to enter the tournament finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I am pursuing is not the usual tournament prestige or glory, rather it is {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already won your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need anymore Puzzle Cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want to show him that not everything can go the way he wants it to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Duel start!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First up is the Ninja Commander Ikusa in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Ninja Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another Ninja just appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the Ninja Commander remains in face-up Attack Mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon one Ninja Soldier from my hand in Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe such a conceited Hollywood star would play such weak and boring Monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on his first turn, and still brag about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Amazoness Swords Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazoness Slash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? Magnum seems really weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem like a star at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you! Don't ruin my image of the ninja hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I expected of you, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly have powered up since our last encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn. Draw card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Commander Ikusa in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then Special Summon Ninja Soldier Katana!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just as repetitive as ever, whether you're acting or Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're just as harsh as ever, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that strong personality really turns me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, big brother, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} sure is lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never really thought of her in that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} has a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No {\i1}way{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's only interested in Dueling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And no man alive can put up with that arrogant personality of hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That {\b0}idiot{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What ever is the matter? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that without you telling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazoness Swords Woman! Take care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazoness Slash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}, I have been waiting for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to Summon Ninja Master Shogun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Ninja Commander and the Ninja Soldier must both be in the Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sacrifice my remaining Ninja Soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Summon Ninja Master Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Master Shogun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have some kind of Special Effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Ninja Master is Summoned using the Commander and Soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:11:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he holds the Ability to Special Summon two more Ninjas from my deck in Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Ninja Commander Kabuki I just Summoned in Attack Mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...allows me to Special Summon Ninja Lady Soldier in Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, will Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. This isn't enough to stop a Duelist like Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Monster's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Ninja Master Shogun to attack Amazoness Sword Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireball Art!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ninjas, now that she has no more Wall Monsters, sneak in for a Direct Attack on Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell am I {\b0}doing{\b1}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}, please do not think badly of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It mortifies me to attack my loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But love is a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this burning feeling throbbing inside my chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just let me guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?! This ain't like you, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} is seriously gonna have to marry this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one reverse card.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Concentrate, concentrate...! If I can't enter the finals because of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it won't be a joking matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Cyber Lady - Cyber Bondage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the law of battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you wanna beat your enemy, you start with the boss first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scratch Clash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Trap, activate! Ninja Art: Smoke Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Trap Card Ninja Art: Smoke Bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,protects me from one of your Monsters' attacks for the duration of the turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that card for {\i1}real{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a one reverse card,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear it, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}? Our wedding march, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean the march of grievance at your {\i1}funeral{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still lovely even when you're mouthing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my victory has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment Magic-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ninja Art{\i0}: Great Kite of Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Kite of Ninja is one of the "Ninja Secret Arts" that can only be used with Ninja Master Shogu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No Monster or Magic Cards can touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, due to it's Special Effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the opponent has a Wall Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by sacrificing one of your own Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can directly attack your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Ninja Soldier and Katana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Art!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just skip this meaningless Duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and start talking about our honeymoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes on, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} will become his bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi ,is there no other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} draws the Harpie's Feather Duster from her deck, she may be able to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:15:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai, do you have the Harpie's Feather Duster in your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've {\i1}used{\i0} it if I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then use your coercive personality to overcome the impossible and draw it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how'd it go? Were you able to draw Harpie's Feather Duster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no other way, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about the Ninja Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there's no sacrifices for the Ninja Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he can't attack with the Great Kite of Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mai! Just stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't {\i1}you{\i0} calm down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there's no Monster sacrifices for the Ninja Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he shouldn't be able to use the Great Kite of Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This is an official Duel, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advice is strictly prohibited!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's still three Ninjas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} has only {\i1}one{\i0} Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not looking good for Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So eventually it will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just do your best, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have the time to waste here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the tournament finals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}know{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Friends, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Card, Kaleidoscope - Magnificent Replication!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this card to make clones of my Harpie Ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scratch Clash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D'oh! Goddamn boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy? You talking about {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mature woman like Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} doesn't fit a {\i1}child{\i0} like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you to stay out of us adult's romance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I deserve to be with Mai too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was speaking hypothetically. {\i1}Hypothetically{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm both rich and powerful and a Hollywood star.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from your appearance, you're a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to see that who is qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so damn {\i1}arrogant{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hollywood this, Hollywood that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your movies earned, like, nothing in the box office and aren't even well-known!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are almost all B-level films!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, didn't you just say you were Magnum-{\i1}san{\i0}'s fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, that was {\i1}before{\i0} he started talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you may say,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if I play a Monster next turn for a Sacrifice Summon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card. My turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.75,0:17:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Ninja Master can directly attack Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card Early Burial!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no longer have a Monster to sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna strip you of your stardom right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While seemingly perfect, Ninja Master has one major weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the Great Kite of Ninja remains in the sky, Ninja Master can't be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, he can't count as a Wall Monster to {\i1}defend{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning right now you don't have any Wall Monsters on the field to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie Ladies! Direct Attack the player!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triple Scratch Clash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The match is over, mister Hollywood star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no "happy ending" in {\i1}real{\i0} life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the shock of losing was too much for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a drama is close to the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is always a huge turn-around that shocks you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even have any Life lef-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The duel is over, so why didn't it disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a solid vision! It's {\i1}real{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hollywood Illusion!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let... let me go! You cheapskate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I couldn't win Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} in a Duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be taking Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} with me by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, bring Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} down immediately! 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said {\i1}let me go{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stunt man, hurry up and save Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}! What the heck are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'll catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Jounouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}, I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always relying on your stunt doubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... my love is sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should at least save the woman you love with your {\i1}own{\i0} hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, this "boy" looks like more of a hero than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have... lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really alright to blow such a big chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's tons of men out there who'd love to have a nice woman like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean "there's not many men who can handle a feisty woman like me.", don't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stage of the finals is right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(141,139)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally arrived at the stadium under construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.28,0:21:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... is this really the stage of the tournament finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But participants in the tournament finals show up one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namu-{\i1}kun{\i0}? Even Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, Malik finally appears before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, a giant blimp appears before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:22:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? The true stage of the finals is this {\i1}blimp{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time! "The Battle Ship Takes Off!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like I've been here, been in this place before
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.81,0:22:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the classroom shaded by the setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I laughed along and pointed with my too shortly cut bangs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.33,0:22:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Little by little, time keeps going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:23:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My bangs now over my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sunset took everyone together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure nothing changed while we were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.44,0:23:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I kept on searching for something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you understood such a senseless time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From here, always...
